Subject: Re: [VB] Cool tin?

Jake Raby has done extensive testing and found the "cool tins"  raised
engine temps in every application he put them in.

They came from Type III's, i'd leave them in Type III's. They are not
designed to work with the Type 1 cooling system.

Eric Allred
Aircooled.Net


